## Exit Criteria (Per Feature)

- [ ] All screens from UX_SPEC implemented
- [ ] API integration working against real endpoints (not mocks)
- [ ] All UI states handled (loading, error, empty, success)
- [ ] Responsive at all specified breakpoints
- [ ] Forms validate and handle errors
- [ ] Keyboard accessible, ARIA labels present
- [ ] COMPONENT_SPEC.md updated with new components
- [ ] Code follows coding standards (files <800 lines, immutable patterns)
- [ ] Verification-loop report passes
